    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357380/extras/3c4fa0638677c9451eb1e92dbc974caf.poster.avif?t=1772178769\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357380/extras/3c4fa0638677c9451eb1e92dbc974caf.webm?t=1772178769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >那些怪物是你不愿回想的秘密，如今却再度出现</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《八爪的秘密：海洋之秘》这款动作角色扮演独立游戏的诞生是为了致敬电子游戏的GBA时代，作为《八爪先生救救我！》的精神续作，将带玩家进入全然不同的时代，章鱼这个种族的历史已被抹除。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >章鱼与人类的战争结束之后，和平共处了数百年。如今，世界必须面对来自过去的秘密。野生动物慢慢消失，神秘的秩序神庙日渐强大，各国关系愈发紧张，陆上也频频出现暗影虚空。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357380/extras/3f27f44d6c0c8042bf26ddb1d652ee9e.poster.avif?t=1772178769\" width=600 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357380/extras/3f27f44d6c0c8042bf26ddb1d652ee9e.webm?t=1772178769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357380/extras/3f27f44d6c0c8042bf26ddb1d652ee9e.mp4?t=1772178769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357380/extras/d6461adea22c9e33e0e75dce38584177.poster.avif?t=1772178769\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357380/extras/d6461adea22c9e33e0e75dce38584177.webm?t=1772178769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357380/extras/d6461adea22c9e33e0e75dce38584177.mp4?t=1772178769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 化身六个角色，各有各的技能和共生能力。了解他们各自的故事，克服他们的心理创伤，为这个世界带来积极的改变。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357380/extras/e5e8a2816c69ec362f2eb7d63407bbc4.poster.avif?t=1772178769\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357380/extras/e5e8a2816c69ec362f2eb7d63407bbc4.webm?t=1772178769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357380/extras/e5e8a2816c69ec362f2eb7d63407bbc4.mp4?t=1772178769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 从前的英雄章鱼如今可以与你同行，教会他们咒术，就能助你战斗或者助你破解谜题。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357380/extras/3228c00f0fe5f88c5381bdfb2017ee1d.poster.avif?t=1772178769\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357380/extras/3228c00f0fe5f88c5381bdfb2017ee1d.webm?t=1772178769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357380/extras/3228c00f0fe5f88c5381bdfb2017ee1d.mp4?t=1772178769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 即时战斗模式，即时构思策略，对抗陆上肆虐的暗影怪物。针对敌人的弱点切换不同的角色，以此占据上风，还可以选择新的装备提升自身的战力。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357380/extras/9892b814e97973b04193b21535b38261.poster.avif?t=1772178769\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357380/extras/9892b814e97973b04193b21535b38261.webm?t=1772178769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357380/extras/9892b814e97973b04193b21535b38261.mp4?t=1772178769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 探索广阔而又纷乱的世界，往返陆上各地，了解过去的秘密。踏上精彩的冒险之旅，发现暗影之乱的真相，邂逅令人难忘的角色，恢复这个世界的光明。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
